rows.label: tev060601_MSG0001
rows.name:
Before city, Pirapira only have to hunt around and
catch vagabond ants and cetecegem beetles in order
to enjoy tasty meal.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060601_MSG0002
rows.name:
But here in city, food cost moneyâ€”and human friends

rows.label: tev060601_MSG0003
rows.name:
Only safe haven is this bin. If Pirapira wait here,
nice friends deliver many fine things to eat![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060601_MSG0004
rows.name:
Box is food heaven. Except for sometimes when tummy
start to hurt really bad and then...terrible things.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060601_MSG0005
rows.name: Ugh. Pirapira want to eat real food one day.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060601_MSG0008
rows.name:
Pirapira was so excited about friendship treaty.
Pirapira heard that friends could come to New LA
and gorge selves on acres of delicious food...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060601_MSG0009
rows.name: But no one told Pirapira that food costs money! Meh![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060601_MSG0010
rows.name:
Pirapira blew entire savings on Miralife Cards right
after moving here and went flat broke. *ruuuumble*[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060601_MSG0011
rows.name:
Now Pirapira going to die ironic death with amazing
Miralife Cards in hand but no food in stomach.
Meeeeeeeh...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060601_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Pirapira about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060601_MSG0012
rows.name: Did friend know this bin is called GARBAGE bin?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060601_MSG0013
rows.name:
...Friend KNEW?! Why did friend not say something
and stop Pirapira from engaging in stomach-turning
bin binge?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060601_MSG0014
rows.name:
Also, human friends should be ashamed for throwing
out food that can still be eaten when...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060601_MSG0015
rows.name:
Wait! Pirapira could put food from bin into cans and
sell it to caravans for big money! It genius![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060601_MSG0016
rows.name:
Nopon customer not need to know finer details like
where food come from or what it actually made of.
All is local! Organic! Farm to bin to table![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060601_MSG0019
rows.name:
Pirapira decided to sell off less-rare Miralife Cards
and use money to buy first proper meal in long time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060601_MSG0020
rows.name:
Now that Pirapira not hunched over in digestive
agony, Pirapira can go back to being merchant and
save money for cards AND food![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060601_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Pirapira about recent developments.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060601_MSG0021
rows.name:
Thanks to generosity of friend, Pirapira able to eat
something good for once and say good-bye to
gastrointestinal hell.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060601_MSG0022
rows.name:
...What? Pirapira should also say good-bye to Miralife
Card addiction? Meh! Never![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev060601_MSG0023
rows.name:
Pirapira going to make it as merchant and earn
enough to buy food AND cards! Friend just watch![ST:wait ]
